'''Studio Keel''', also credited as '''Keel''', is Serbian clothing company specializing in swimwear for [[water polo]], swimming and recreation for men and woman.
== History == Keel is established by Serbian water polo player [[Andrija Prlainović]]<ref>[http://sport.blic.rs/ostali-sportovi/vitrine-pune-pehara-prlainovic-za-blicsport-i-ovo-ce-biti-leto-medalja/sypcn1b VITRINE PUNE PEHARA Prlainović za Blicsport: I ovo će biti leto medalja], [[Blic]]</ref> in 2014.<ref>[http://www.novosti.rs/vesti/sport.297.html:496191-Andrija-Prlainovic-predstavio-robnu-marku-Keel Andrija Prlainović predstavio robnu marku Keel!]</ref>
